{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tutorial-js","path":"/zh/tutorial/Visualization/AdvanceSetting/AdvanceSetting/","webpackCompilationHash":"b56fc1f276773fcd7503","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>该板块将会介绍如何对地图进行合理的优化。</p>\n<h3 id=\"调整图层顺序\"><a href=\"#%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E5%9B%BE%E5%B1%82%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>调整图层顺序</h3>\n<p>介绍调整图层顺序的原则和方法，达到优化地图的目的。</p>\n<h3 id=\"设置图层可见比例尺范围\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%9B%BE%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%81%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%BA%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设置图层可见比例尺范围</h3>\n<p>通过介绍如何为图层设置最大可见比例尺和最小可见比例尺范围，对地图图层显示效果进行优化。</p>\n<h3 id=\"过滤显示地图中的对象\"><a href=\"#%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>过滤显示地图中的对象</h3>\n<p>通过设置过滤条件将图层中的对象进行过滤，显示那些符合条件的对象，提供地图显示的速度。</p>\n<h3 id=\"设置显示对象的最小尺寸\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8F%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设置显示对象的最小尺寸</h3>\n<p>为当前图层设置对象显示的最小尺寸，小于最小尺寸的对象将不再显示，进而提升地图显示的速度。</p>\n<h3 id=\"设置最大可见节点数\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%81%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%95%B0\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设置最大可见节点数</h3>\n<p>为当前图层中当前地图中对象显示的节点数目进行限制。对于超出最大节点数目的对象将不予显示，可以加速地图的显示速度。</p>\n<h3 id=\"优化点符号显示\"><a href=\"#%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E7%82%B9%E7%AC%A6%E5%8F%B7%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>优化点符号显示</h3>\n<p>点符号的显示效果可以通过启用符号缩放(SymbolZoom.htm)以及使用固定符号角度(FixSymAngle.htm)两种方式进行优化。</p>\n<h3 id=\"优化线型显示\"><a href=\"#%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E7%BA%BF%E5%9E%8B%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>优化线型显示</h3>\n<p>线性显示效果的优化，可以通过启用线型反走样(LineAntialiasing.htm)、显示完整线型(Linedisplay.htm)和十字路口优化(RoadCross.htm)方式进行优化。</p>\n<h3 id=\"优化文本显示\"><a href=\"#%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>优化文本显示</h3>\n<p>优化文本显示效果的方式有多种，过滤地图中的压盖文本(OverlapObj.htm)、启用文本反走样(TextAntialiasing.htm)、固定文本角度(FixTextAngle.htm)、固定文本方向(FixTextOrientation.htm)以及对文本的尺寸范围(VisiableRanges.htm)进行设置。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"优化地图显示效果","next":null,"prev":null},"fields":{"path":"content\\tutorial\\Visualization\\AdvanceSetting\\AdvanceSetting.zh.md","slug":"/zh/tutorial/Visualization/AdvanceSetting/AdvanceSetting/","langKey":"zh"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/zh/tutorial/Visualization/AdvanceSetting/AdvanceSetting/"}}}